title: Jelly Part 2: Counteracting Self Destruction and His Songs Going Gold
itunes:title: Jelly Part 2: Counteracting Self Destruction and His Songs Going Gold
description:
Jelly continues his convo with Bunnie this week, talking about the musical family they have built up over the years and how amazing it is to see everyone thriving. He also talks about hitting a billion views on YouTube, how he shot his foot, and the way artists really make money these days. Bunnie shares what she really thought of him the first time they met.
